  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "SpriteKit is largely a single threaded game engine and as such the API provides developers with callbacks to implement your custom game logic. The primary callback for your game logic is "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/spritekit/skscenedelegate/1519757-update"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". Other callbacks are illustrated in "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "link-media-2527821"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". Modifying SpriteKit objects outside of the scene delegate callbacks (such as in a background queue or anything else not running on the main thread) can result in concurrency related problems. Even dispatching work on the main thread asynchronously or at a later time is risky because the closure is likely to be done outside of the timeframe SpriteKit expects. If you're experiencing a segmentation fault or other type of crash occurring deep within the SpriteKit framework, there's a good chance your code is modifying a SpriteKit object outside of the scene delegate callbacks. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "aside",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "To check at runtime if a particular block of code is running on the main thread, inspect "
                },
                {
                  "type": "link",
                  "title": "NSThread",
                  "destination": "https://developer.apple.com/library/archive/releasenotes/Foundation/RN-FoundationOlderNotes/index.html#//apple_ref/doc/uid/TP40008080-TRANSLATED_CHAPTER_965-TRANSLATED_DEST_130"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/nsthread/1408455-ismainthread"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ". "
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "style": "note",
          "name": "Note"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": []
        }
      ]
